{"tid":2303820,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"伊拉克爆發宗派衝突 至少4死51傷","createTime":"2020-11-28T09:05:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T09:12:25.000Z","uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"421deb064fa730f6a2d80b02310d70ac0faca419","tid":2303820,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:05:42.000Z","msg":"伊拉克什葉派教士薩德爾（Muqtada Al-Sadr）的支持者周五（27日）在首都巴格達及南部城市納西里耶示威，要求國家進行政治改革。<strong><span class=\"red\">在納西里耶，薩德爾的支持者與反政府示威者爆發衝突，造成4死51傷，部分人受槍傷。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n薩德爾什葉派政黨「薩德爾運動」的始創人，日前揚言其領導的政黨會在明年6月的提前大選，將推動由該黨成員任新總理。他的支持者周五響應號召到上述兩地示威，並在納西里耶遇到在當地紮營的反政府人士。反政府示威者指控薩德爾支持者持槍，並破壞及放火燒帳幕，現場冒出大量黑煙。<strong><span class=\"red\">衝突導致多人死傷，其中9人有槍傷。在巴格達，數以萬計的薩德爾支持者聚集在解放廣場，有人持薩德爾的畫像。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GZtF7Wk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGZtF7Wk.jpg&h=4a33d88a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n薩德爾是伊拉克什葉派穆斯林的領袖之一，也是什葉派政黨「薩德爾運動」和武裝組織「邁赫迪軍」的創立者和領導者，他在2003年伊拉克戰爭之後迅速崛起的一名伊拉克政治家<strong><span class=\"red\">，其主張在伊拉克建立伊斯蘭神治政權，薩達姆倒台後，他成立武裝組織邁赫迪軍（Mehdi Army）對抗美軍及伊拉克政府，華府視之為伊拉克安全最大威脅。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">2018年伊拉克大選，他帶領的什葉派政黨「向改革前進」聯盟，以宗教及反貪為口號異軍成功突起，左右伊拉克政局發展，也為動盪的中東局勢再增添不安。<br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"cc07c2b0115ba4fae563f7e8ea685c6e2e8200f1","tid":2303820,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:06:29.000Z","msg":"有點當年伊朗伊斯蘭革介既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb9bb547541b6d097d26169b2aac6d41d4de8dc","tid":2303820,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:06:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/11/27/tens-of-thousands-of-sadr-supporters-rally-in-baghdad\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2020%2F11%2F27%2Ftens-of-thousands-of-sadr-supporters-rally-in-baghdad&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CuxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=6f0294ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/11/27/tens-of-thousands-of-sadr-supporters-rally-in-baghdad</a>"},{"pid":"c34c8120abec5b9e446289500a106030dbc4f629","tid":2303820,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:07:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e55f908900b16cec673ac392723bd5ba8b83f8ae","tid":2303820,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c34c8120abec5b9e446289500a106030dbc4f629","tid":2303820,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:07:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:08:48.000Z","msg":"發展程度低、教育程度低、窮、貪污、戰亂、保守思想根深柢固<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c342e8c85e0da446a807c439fe91f9c523a22e0b","tid":2303820,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}